---
title: Pan-Seared Pork with Onion Gravy, Broccolini and Buttery Mashed Potatoes
description: We’ve infused a delicious gravy with sweet red onion and fragrant rosemary and drizzled it over pan-seared pork. Creamy mashed potatoes also soak up all that gravy goodness. This is comfort food at its finest!
